id: pm-70mi
title: "Agent-UX combined PR: compact mutation output (pm-ch59) + smarter unknown-flag recovery (pm-8nyc)"
description: "Combined PR delivering two agent-UX/token-efficiency items under pm-rnpb. (A) pm-ch59: shared mutation-result projection helper that drops mutation-envelope changed_fields arrays (keeps changed_field_count) — wired to a CLI --no-changed-fields global flag and made the MCP agent path compact-by-default unless the MCP-level fullChangedFields control is set. The projector intentionally preserves non-mutation/user changed_fields metadata. (B) pm-8nyc: prefix/abbreviation-aware nearest-flag suggestions, cross-command flag awareness hints, and --sort value aliases (updated->updated_at, created->created_at) for list/list-all. Integrated, full-coverage gated, dogfooded, changelog regenerated via pm-changelog, shipped as one PR with green CI + AI bot review."
type: Plan
status: closed
priority: 2
tags[4]: agent-ux,dogfood,dx,pm-cli
