  "2026-05-26T14:42:06.541Z",codex-review-continuation,"Evidence: addressed latest PR #72 Codex review feedback. Projection now only compacts mutation envelopes plus update-many apply/rollback rows, preserving nested/user changed_fields metadata and non-mutation payloads. MCP full changed_fields control moved to fullChangedFields so mutation options.full is forwarded unchanged. Verification passed: pm linked focused test (34 tests), direct node scripts/run-tests.mjs focused suite (34 tests), pnpm build, pnpm quality:static."
  "2026-05-26T14:57:25.379Z",codex-review-continuation,"Evidence: fixed remote coverage failure by adding the missing update-many apply rows-without-changed_fields branch regression. Verification passed locally: node scripts/run-tests.mjs coverage (1825 tests, 100% statements/branches/functions/lines)."
  "2026-05-26T15:11:10.472Z",codex-review-continuation,"Evidence: addressed latest CodeRabbit/Gemini review follow-up. Rows rewrite now preserves null-prototype update-many envelopes, fullChangedFields is reserved from dynamic extension passthrough, and withMutationCompaction accepts missing options. Verification passed: focused mutation/MCP suite (19 tests) and node scripts/run-tests.mjs coverage (1826 tests, 100% statements/branches/functions/lines)."
